## Description {#details}

This is an entry in the NonLocalDepInfo cache.

For each <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/basicblock">BasicBlock</a> (the BB entry) it keeps a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/memdepresult">MemDepResult</a>.
